{"ocr_results":[{"text":"these selected constant price products.","box":[[184,186],[905,188],[905,212],[184,210]]},{"text":"Constant price is an accounting","box":[[907,190],[1451,190],[1451,214],[907,214]]},{"text":"figure.","box":[[185,223],[345,223],[345,247],[185,247]]},{"text":"When they set these targets for costs they set a percentage","box":[[335,220],[1384,224],[1383,251],[335,247]]},{"text":"for reducing costs in producing","box":[[181,254],[736,256],[736,283],[181,281]]},{"text":" the set product.","box":[[726,258],[1068,259],[1068,283],[725,282]]},{"text":"The constant price","box":[[1063,260],[1381,260],[1381,284],[1063,284]]},{"text":"product is just one of several products that may be produced in a plant.","box":[[180,290],[1452,292],[1452,321],[180,319]]},{"text":"They don't set cost targets for all products, just selected ones.","box":[[182,326],[1367,328],[1367,356],[182,354]]},{"text":"So","box":[[1362,333],[1398,333],[1398,352],[1362,352]]},{"text":"this is a way of competing with advanced units.","box":[[183,362],[1034,363],[1034,390],[183,389]]},{"text":"The state will.select","box":[[1046,365],[1416,365],[1416,388],[1046,388]]},{"text":"certain constant price products","box":[[184,399],[735,400],[735,424],[184,423]]},{"text":"s to be the targeted ones and then set","box":[[722,401],[1384,401],[1384,425],[722,425]]},{"text":"targets for costs which is the amount to be reduced.","box":[[184,435],[1095,435],[1095,459],[184,459]]},{"text":"Funds (zijin)--this is not a target, but just a figure of funds","box":[[250,468],[1364,469],[1364,496],[250,495]]},{"text":"supplied by the state to a plant.","box":[[183,505],[792,505],[792,532],[183,532]]},{"text":"It is calculated by the bureau","box":[[800,507],[1328,507],[1328,531],[800,531]]},{"text":"based on the amount of products in the output targets.","box":[[179,538],[1139,541],[1139,568],[179,565]]},{"text":"The bureau","box":[[1171,541],[1347,541],[1347,565],[1171,565]]},{"text":"has the responsibility for apportioning state funds to the factories","box":[[181,575],[1382,575],[1382,602],[181,602]]},{"text":"under it.","box":[[184,611],[377,611],[377,632],[184,632]]},{"text":"It gets a fixed amount each year, through the bank system,","box":[[373,610],[1398,612],[1398,639],[373,637]]},{"text":"and it distributes the money to factories based on the targets of production","box":[[182,643],[1524,644],[1524,674],[182,673]]},{"text":"for each plant.","box":[[183,679],[468,680],[467,707],[183,706]]},{"text":"The responsibility for apportioning this money--estimating","box":[[484,681],[1504,681],[1504,708],[484,708]]},{"text":"and calculating needs--was that of his own bureau finance department.","box":[[185,717],[1396,717],[1396,741],[185,741]]},{"text":"While deciding, plant directors are all called to the bureau for a meeting,","box":[[180,748],[1504,750],[1504,780],[180,778]]},{"text":"and then later, if the plant director thinks of something else, he will come","box":[[182,786],[1524,785],[1524,812],[182,813]]},{"text":"back to the bureau and talk with their department head individually.","box":[[183,823],[1377,823],[1377,847],[183,847]]},{"text":"Guanxi does not count here.","box":[[182,859],[671,859],[671,883],[182,883]]},{"text":"They have a fixed formula for apportioning","box":[[696,859],[1435,859],[1435,883],[696,883]]},{"text":"the funds, based on output targets.","box":[[184,893],[803,896],[803,920],[184,917]]},{"text":"They can use this because the products","box":[[835,894],[1504,892],[1504,919],[835,921]]},{"text":"the factories under their bureau produced are all the same--steel. Once","box":[[181,927],[1456,926],[1456,956],[181,957]]},{"text":"the funds are spent, you don't pay them back--they're gone. But all the","box":[[183,963],[1454,961],[1454,991],[183,993]]},{"text":"plant profit goes back to the bureau.","box":[[182,1001],[835,1000],[835,1027],[182,1028]]},{"text":"Funds Management","box":[[183,1072],[469,1072],[469,1096],[183,1096]]},{"text":"(6/11/80, 2 hrs.)","box":[[502,1072],[796,1072],[796,1096],[502,1096]]},{"text":"Funds are divided into two types.","box":[[251,1103],[839,1107],[839,1134],[251,1130]]},{"text":"Circulating funds, and fixed funds.","box":[[873,1106],[1482,1104],[1482,1128],[873,1130]]},{"text":"Both are invested by the state.","box":[[183,1141],[730,1141],[730,1165],[183,1165]]},{"text":"Fixed funds (guding zijin) are invested","box":[[765,1141],[1454,1138],[1454,1165],[765,1167]]},{"text":"in fixed capital and machinery.","box":[[183,1174],[730,1176],[729,1203],[183,1201]]},{"text":"These funds are dead (si).1","box":[[766,1174],[1265,1173],[1265,1200],[766,1201]]},{"text":"But circulating","box":[[1254,1171],[1522,1175],[1521,1202],[1253,1198]]},{"text":"funds are live (huo), they move","box":[[186,1210],[731,1213],[730,1237],[185,1234]]},{"text":"around.","box":[[765,1214],[925,1210],[925,1233],[765,1237]]},{"text":"Fixed funds include machinery","box":[[919,1206],[1436,1210],[1436,1239],[919,1236]]},{"text":"and plant buildings.","box":[[184,1247],[538,1247],[538,1274],[184,1274]]},{"text":"The circulating funds are used to buy materials","box":[[569,1244],[1415,1245],[1415,1272],[569,1271]]},{"text":"parts, electricity, transport, and labor.","box":[[179,1281],[913,1278],[913,1308],[179,1311]]},{"text":"At the end of the year the","box":[[942,1280],[1398,1280],[1398,1304],[942,1304]]},{"text":"excess funds over the fixed amount for circulating funds is profit,","box":[[182,1315],[1365,1313],[1365,1343],[182,1345]]},{"text":"and that is all remitted to the state.","box":[[184,1353],[855,1352],[856,1376],[184,1377]]},{"text":"If the production targets are","box":[[883,1351],[1400,1350],[1400,1377],[883,1378]]},{"text":"raised for the next year, the plant will be given an increment to its","box":[[183,1386],[1399,1385],[1399,1413],[183,1414]]},{"text":"stock of circulating funds.","box":[[182,1422],[675,1421],[675,1448],[182,1449]]},{"text":"If the","box":[[695,1422],[807,1425],[807,1450],[694,1447]]},{"text":"equota decreases,they","box":[[793,1423],[1195,1421],[1195,1448],[793,1450]]},{"text":" take away from","box":[[1182,1422],[1453,1422],[1453,1446],[1182,1446]]},{"text":"plant funds.","box":[[182,1458],[418,1456],[418,1483],[183,1485]]},{"text":"Circulating funds are constantly circulating through the","box":[[428,1458],[1418,1455],[1418,1482],[428,1485]]},{"text":"M-C-M (money-commodities-money) chain.","box":[[181,1492],[855,1493],[854,1520],[181,1519]]},{"text":"Losing money (kuiben). T","box":[[250,1527],[690,1524],[690,1557],[250,1560]]},{"text":"There are two ways to operate at a loss.","box":[[673,1528],[1379,1525],[1380,1552],[673,1555]]},{"text":"The first is 'planned loss' (jihua kuiben).","box":[[182,1562],[945,1561],[945,1588],[182,1589]]},{"text":"Articles will be produced at","box":[[977,1562],[1471,1562],[1471,1586],[977,1586]]},{"text":"a cost above their state-set selling price, because it is decided to keep","box":[[181,1596],[1472,1594],[1472,1625],[181,1627]]},{"text":"the price of that article low for the next step in the production","box":[[185,1633],[1330,1631],[1330,1658],[185,1660]]},{"text":"process, meaning the next set of enterprises","box":[[182,1672],[965,1667],[965,1694],[183,1699]]},{"text":"s in the product chain.","box":[[952,1669],[1349,1669],[1349,1693],[952,1693]]},{"text":"So","box":[[1381,1669],[1419,1669],[1419,1692],[1381,1692]]},{"text":"each year the state will make","box":[[183,1706],[698,1705],[698,1729],[183,1730]]},{"text":"up","box":[[691,1708],[754,1708],[754,1729],[691,1729]]},{"text":") the planned","box":[[742,1706],[964,1704],[964,1728],[742,1730]]},{"text":"deficit infunds.","box":[[955,1704],[1318,1702],[1318,1725],[955,1727]]},{"text":"This","box":[[1314,1704],[1380,1704],[1380,1726],[1314,1726]]},{"text":"is planned such that a bureau loses money in","box":[[183,1739],[964,1738],[964,1766],[183,1767]]},{"text":"1 one plant but makes it in","box":[[955,1741],[1418,1737],[1418,1761],[955,1765]]},{"text":"another, and overall it should balance out.","box":[[183,1775],[940,1774],[940,1801],[183,1802]]},{"text":"The second kind is","box":[[254,1813],[572,1813],[572,1837],[254,1837]]},{"text":"s'unplanned loss'(fei jihua kuiben).","box":[[563,1810],[1263,1808],[1263,1835],[563,1837]]},{"text":"Thismostoften","box":[[1261,1811],[1525,1811],[1525,1834],[1261,1834]]},{"text":"happens when the state has a plant which it recognizes will not make much","box":[[182,1847],[1474,1843],[1474,1871],[182,1875]]},{"text":"money and gives low profit targets to.1","box":[[181,1884],[898,1881],[898,1908],[181,1911]]},{"text":"If the plant misses by a little,","box":[[884,1881],[1455,1883],[1455,1910],[884,1908]]},{"text":"they lose money.","box":[[187,1921],[469,1921],[469,1945],[187,1945]]},{"text":"This is the fault of the plant management.","box":[[500,1917],[1246,1918],[1246,1945],[500,1944]]},{"text":"This influences","box":[[1278,1915],[1545,1918],[1545,1945],[1278,1942]]},{"text":"their stock of circulating","box":[[183,1952],[647,1954],[647,1981],[183,1979]]},{"text":"g capitalï¼Œ reduces it and it is not enough to","box":[[633,1954],[1422,1954],[1422,1981],[633,1981]]},{"text":"produce the same quota of products","box":[[180,1991],[788,1990],[788,2017],[180,2018]]},{"text":"s the next year.","box":[[774,1991],[1057,1992],[1057,2016],[774,2015]]},{"text":"They have no other recourse","box":[[1084,1990],[1564,1990],[1564,2017],[1084,2017]]},{"text":"but to borrow from the bank.","box":[[182,2027],[715,2027],[715,2051],[182,2051]]},{"text":"There is interest on these loans.","box":[[712,2027],[1322,2027],[1322,2051],[712,2051]]},{"text":"Butfirst","box":[[1330,2028],[1491,2028],[1491,2049],[1330,2049]]},{"text":"a work team will be dispatched to inspect the plant, usually quality problems","box":[[181,2062],[1546,2061],[1546,2088],[181,2089]]},{"text":"are the cause of losses, because the plant can't sell its products.","box":[[182,2097],[1371,2098],[1371,2125],[182,2124]]},{"text":"Ifa","box":[[1402,2098],[1476,2098],[1476,2123],[1402,2123]]},{"text":"-5-","box":[[837,2149],[892,2149],[892,2179],[837,2179]]}],"dimensions":{"height":2207,"width":1580}}